<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Raluvin</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-06-08 08:20:33</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>All nastiness aside, the Red Dragonscale is as suggested dropped off a dragon, in this instance Nagafen.  This is a far superior piece of armour for a warrior than the BEBP.  <BR>
<BR>
Items Req:  Red Dragonscale - Naggy<BR>
Vial of Swirling Mist - U/K<BR>
1000pp<BR>
<BR>
You take all this stuff to the guy at Human Inn in Rathe Mountains(who you must have high faction with)and have him make it for u.  It is believed that Wolf Form is sufficient for you to deal with him.<BR>
<BR>
Btw - what the hell is a tank doing with a yak at lvl 35 anyways?? they are totally counter productive until 37</font></td></tr></table>
